<p>This perfect combination of modern and historic architecture makes Toronto a very enjoyable city to walk in, despite its traffic and high density of tall office buildings.</p>
<h2>Ripley's Aquarium of Canada</h2>
<p>After a long day's walk in the streets of Toronto, an indoor activity is always welcome. In the CN Tower's shadow lies the <a href="https://www.ripleyaquariums.com/canada/">Ripley's Aquarium of Canada</a>, whose most famous attraction is this underwater tunnel where sharks and rays can be observed, among others.</p>
